While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money, you took this milk job first before your parents bought it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Was that your first part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did your parents pay you when you helped them or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No. Well I got pocket money and then all me food and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 You did that for love did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 This first milk job that you got, how did you get that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
Well the lady - yes, well the lady was - they had people going round and she - somebody said, Mrs Walker wants someone to take the milk. This lady - this girl was leaving or something. So I applied. Think you get very much. 
Seven or eight shillings a week I think it would be in those days. Wasn't very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 You just delivered the milk did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 What hours did you work when you first took it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Well about an hour and a half before you went to school. An
d then - when you came from school at the evening. Five o'clockish, yes, about an hour. Except -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 And you worked on .....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes. Oh and they didn't have - no, it was - I think it was once day then, I think it only came once a day when it was the war time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 And you worked Saturdays and Sundays as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you have a half day off, any days off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No. That's the only snag with milk businesses.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did they pay you for holidays - how long were you there before your parents took the business over?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh - just about six months I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you have any holidays in that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 You say you were paid seven or eight shillings, did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Well I don't know, in those days 
I think it was - something to have your own pocket money wasn't it. It's like the same as boys now, they go with milk - with paper rounds don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you give any of that money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Do you know what you spent it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh I'd be buying things. Finery, a coat or something or - something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 You'd just spend it on yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 How did you get on with the other people you worked with, did you work with anyone in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No, 
I think there was just me that sent round. The lady was in the house I know. We had a - we worked the round up later and had a much bigger business you know than what we had then. It was only about - ten gallon to deliver I think all together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
Oh she was all right. She was - an old - elderly person. She was - had been a widow for years. She had a family of lodgers, her daughter couldn't go out. Her daughter did the cooking for the lodgers and - she - was it - a st
aid - a staid sort of a character this person was. Bit gruff, you know, she didn't seem - well at first she was O.K. but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 How did you feel about the work, did you like it or dislike it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No I liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did the job alter your attitude to school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you do any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 And your first full time job would be when your parents had the milk business wouldn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 You started working for your parents during the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 When they bought the milk business, is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 So in 1918 you were still working for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you have any other jobs after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh well, yes, to - but that would be after my time
 - that time wouldn't it. Oh. Well - I got a bit browned off with going with the milk. So - one of my customers said she wanted somebody to help her. So - I went two days a week to help, Tuesdays and Fridays, and - I was - housework. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 How old would you be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
Well about sixteen - seventeen. No, seventeen I think. And - she - mother let me keep the money. Tuesdays and Fridays I used to go. And then I went with the milk the other days. And then - that's the only jobs I ever had. Yes. And the
n I went for about two or three years and then I - I came back home again and I was at home - right until I got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Have you done any jobs since you were married apart from teaching music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 So now }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9403854\charrsid6187387 you\rquote re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387  a music teacher, when did you start teaching music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
Oh I started, that's it, I started teaching music before I was married you see. I told you, before, I said, if I couldn't be a teacher I wanted to be a teacher of music. So after I got through me exams - I would start about -
 how old would I be then, about twenty - twenty odd. Twenty - twenty or twenty-one I think hen I started teaching.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 How many pupils did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh I had - quite a lot. Just - just people round the district you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 And you've done that since you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Have you always had pupils then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
Yes. Well - haven't many now. Haven't - very - just friends now. And I'm returned now. For that. I've come into the townswoman now you see so - and usually is all voluntary now aren't they, more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 What jobs have you done since the first world war, it was just helping this person across the road and then teaching music, is that right?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 And I used to play for - for the local dancing school in Darlington. Which I began.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 I still - I still play occasionally - occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 When did you start doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Twenty years now I've been with that. 'Cos my daughter went there you see. I kept it on really thinking she would come back to b
e a teacher but she's not come back. Never came back to Darlington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Would you have preferred another type of occupation or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 I'd rather - I still would have liked to have been a schoolteacher. Loved - I'd have loved to been a schoolteacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
Did you serve an apprenticeship or training period of any of your jobs, obviously for teaching music you did, you went for about six or seven years did you say?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh more than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you belong to a trades union or professional organisation at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you feel at all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 
I'll tell you what I forgot to say. I played, while my daughter was at college, I got the chance to play for the education - a concert party at Eastbourne schools and I played for about three or four yea
rs, just once a week, yes, at concert party. So the money helped -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 When she was at college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 When would this be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Oh - about ten years ago was it. No, more than that, twelve years since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Three or four year - with the Education Authority?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Then - then the - the warden died and they concert party disbanded and I haven't done anything since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different interests that doesn't really apply does it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Because you never went out to business in that sense?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13379731 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 Would you say that work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14690632 LH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11696315\charrsid6187387 No, I don't think so.
